utils.structures

Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • utils.structures.Time

  • public class Time
extends java.lang.Object
    The Time class represents a structure that contains the information about time, and the default minimal time unit is nano-second.
    Author:
    Lingkun Kong, Konstantinos Mamouras
